 needs to operate, maintain, support, and instruct the assets or capabilities; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t14/s1134/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t14/s1134/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft14%2Fs1134%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"prepare an acquisition project or program transition plan to enter into programmatic sustainment, operations, and support.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
